---
title: One-Pot Turkey & Black Bean Chili with Sour Cream & Monterey Jack Cheese
description: A good chili has well-seasoned meat, creamy beans, and tender vegetables. A great chili, however, has all that and comes together in one pot in under an hour. This chili is one of the greats. And once you take a bite, we can guarantee you’ll agree. Not to mention, these porky bowls are adorned with some delicious fixings: tangy sour cream and melty Monterey Jack. If you’ve got some on hand, why not crumble up some tortilla chips and sprinkle them on top for a crunch?
